freBasicOverviewTutorialTitle: Whakanuku kōnae ki tō kōpaki OneDrive
freBasicOverviewTutorialBodyText: Ka taea e koe te tō me te whakataka, te tārua me te whakapiri, te tīpako Nuku rānei ki OneDrive kia tukuatu ki te kapua me te wātea ki ētahi atu pūrere.
freShareFilesTutorialBodyText: Tiria ō kōnae me ō kōpaki mā te pāwhiri-matau me te tīpako ki te tiri.
freShareFilesTutorialBodyTextV2: Tiritiria ō kōnae, kōpaki hoki mā te pāwhiri matau me tīpako i a Tiri. Ki te papapātuhi, whakamahia te Neke+F10, ka tīpako i te kōwhiringa.
freFilesOnDemandTutorialTitleMac: Whakarite mō te wā e tuimotu ai koe
freFilesOnDemandTutorialBodyMac: Mēnā me mahi koe ki tētahi kōnae, me tikiake i mua i te tuimotu.
freFilesOnDemandTutorialMacDownloadHeade: Tikiake i tō kōnae, kōpaki rānei
freFilesOnDemandTutorialMacDownloadDesc: Pāwhiri matauria te kōnae i tō kōpaki OneDrive, ka tautuhi ki Te Pupuri tonu i tēnei Pūrere.
freFilesOnDemandTutorialMacCheckDesc: Kitea ai e koe tēnei ata ki te taha o ngā tūemi e wātea tonu ai i ngā wātea, ahakoa ina kore e āhei koe ki te ipurangi.
freFilesOnDemandTutorialBodyText: Mā ngā Kōnae Ā-Tono, ka taea te tirotiro ō kōnae OneDrive, me te whakatuwhera i ētahi kōnae ahakoa kei te tuimotu koe.
freFilesOnDemandTutorialBodyTextV2: Mā ngā kōnae ina hiahia e taea ai e koe ō kōnae OneDrive te tirotiro, ka whakatuwhera i ētahi kōnae ahakoa tonu he tuimotu koe. Ako atu anō mō ngā kōnae ina hiahia
freMobileUpsellTutorialBodyText: Whakamahia a OneDrive i tētahi waea, paparorohiko rānei hei pūrua i tō rārangi whakaahua kāmera me te tiro i ō kōnae ahako kei hea. E wātea ana mō te iOS me te Android.
freFilesOnDemandOnlineOnlyDesc: He tuihono-anake ngā kōnae whai ata kapua, ā, e kore e whakapau mokowā i tēnei rorohiko kia whakatuwhera rā anō koe
freFilesOnDemandOnlineOnlyDescV2: Kāore e pau i ēnei kōnae te mokowā i tēnei pūrere, ā, ka tikiake i a koe e whakamahia ana.
freFilesOnDemandOnThisDeviceDesc: Ko ngā kōnae whai tohu taki kākāriki ko ngā kōnae kapua kua whakatuwheratia e koe, kia whakapau mokowā ai ināianei ki tēnei rorohiko, ā, ka taea te whakatuwhera tuimotu.
freFilesOnDemandOnThisDeviceDescV2: Ina tuwhera i a koe he kōnae, ka tikiake tērā ki tō pūkoro māu hei whakatika i a koe e tuimotu ana.
freFilesOnDemandAlwaysAvailable: E wātea ana i ngā wā katoa
freFilesOnDemandAlwaysAvailableDesc: He tohu taki kī katoa tō ngā kōnae ina tohu koe i ērā hei "Pupuri tonu i tēnei pūrere". Ka whakapau mokowā ērā i tēnei rorohiko, ā, kei te wātea i ngā wā katoa, akakoa tuimotu
freFilesOnDemandAlwaysAvailableDescV2: Pāwhiria-matau tētahi kōnae kia wātea ai ā-tuimotu.
freRequiredDiagnosticDataTitle: E whakaute ana a Microsoft i tō tūmataiti
freRequiredDiagnosticDataSubTitle: Ina waiho iho tō raraunga ki a OneDrive & Office, ko koe tonu te rangatira o tērā raraunga.
freRequiredDiagnosticDataSubTitleV2: Ina whakawhirinakia e koe ō raraunga ki a OneDrive, ki a Microsoft 365 hoki, nāu tonu hoki aua raraunga.
freRequiredDiagnosticDescPrimary: Ka kohikohia e mātou te raraunga tātaringa kia noho haumaru te OneDrive me Office, kia hōu tonu, kia mahi pērā i tūmanakohia. Kāore i roto i ēnei raraunga tō ingoa, ō ihirangi kōnae, te mōhiohio rānei mō ngā taupānga kāore i pā hāngai.
freRequiredDiagnosticDescPrimaryV2: Ka kohikohia e mātou te raraunga tātaringa e hiahiatia ana kia haumaru tonu ai a OneDrive me Microsoft 365, kia hou tonu ai, kia mahi hoki pērā i tō te tūmanakonga. Kāore i roto i ēnei ko tō ingoa, ō ihirangi kōnae, he ihirangi rānei mō ngā taupānga whaipānga-kore. Ako atu anō mō te kohikohi raraunga tātari
freRequiredDiagnosticDataBodySecondary: Ka tūhono a OneDrive ki ngā ratonga tuihono ki te whakahiko i tō wheako, otiia hei wāhi o tēnā, ka kohia e mātou ngā raraunga ratonga ka hiahiatia. Ka tūhono hoki ērā atu taupānga Office ki ngā ratonga tuihono, e tikiake, e āta tātari hoki i ō ihirangi kia tukua he wheako pai ake. Me whakatika ēnei tautuhinga i roto i ngā taupānga Office.
freRequiredDiagnosticDataBodySecondaryV2: Ka tūhono a OneDrive ki ngā ratonga tuihono ki te whakahiko i ō wheako, otiia hei wāhi o tēnā, ka kohia e mātou ngā raraunga ratonga ka hiahiatia. Ko ērā atu taupānga Microsoft 365 ka tūhono hoki ki ngā ratonga, e tātaritia pea ō ihirangi hei tuku huatau me ngā tūtohutanga.
freOptionalDiagnosticDataDesc: E pai ana mātou kia tiri koe i ngā raraunga tātaritanga me te whakamahinga. He pēhea tā mātou whakapai ake. Kāore he raraunga o tēnei raraunga kei roto i tō ingoa, ō ihirangi kōnae, mōhiohio rānei mō ngā taupānga kāore i tae ki OneDrive me Office.
freOptionalDiagnosticDataDescV2: Tiritiria mai he raraunga tātari, whakamahi hoki hei kōwhiringa kia āwhinahia ai mātou ki te whakapai ake i ō wheako. Kāore i roto i ēnei ko tō ingoa, ō ihirangi kōnae, he mōhiohio rānei mō ngā taupānga e whaipānga-kore ana ki a OneDrive, ki a Microsoft 365 hoki. Ako atu anō mō te kohikohi raraunga tātari

PurchaseSubscriptionTermsBodyAlta: Ka namaia ngā ohaurunga Microsoft 365 ki tō pūkete Itarangi, ā, ka whakahōuhia aunoatia i roto i te 24 hāora i mua i te whakamutunga o te wā ohaurunga o nāianei, engari rawa ka monokia aunoatia anō.
